Sunhawk:  Oh well 3 out of 4 ain't bad.  Just so long
as they're executed soon.

He walked in on Talos and straghtened up in his
presence.

Sunhawk:  Sir I have recieved word that Condor was
unable to locate one of the Predicons although
Grimlock is returning with another, I got an
additional one myself, and Kup will soon return with
some of the energon they were digging up.  And with
all respect sir I don't know about the one your
talking to, but the other Predicon I brought in
doesn't even know where their base is exactly, so it
might be better to eliminate him now than have just be
another enemy later.  With your permission I'll
proceed to do so SIR!

He salutes and waits for and answer.
